Title: 117: 1-on-1 with Kirill: What I learned in 2017
Description:
Welcome to a special episode I bring you before the year ends. I am going to share with you a one-on-one talk about everything I have learned throughout the year 2017, what exactly that meant for me, and also how these learnings changed me as a person. In this episode, I talk about the 6 needs, my personal reflections on 2017, and my insights about the secret to happiness.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/117
